34:17.889 --> 34:21.170
That's my son! Number 19!

34:27.650 --> 34:33.330
- Leon. I am disappointed.
- The courier will be here soon enough.

34:33.409 --> 34:35.370
<i>I have the girl from Tungsten.</i>

34:35.409 --> 34:38.690
I want the reporter's story as
dead as the reporter, you got me?

34:38.770 --> 34:42.330
We have something he
wants. He will come for her.

34:46.449 --> 34:48.330
Who the fuck is this?

34:48.370 --> 34:50.650
I was wondering if I could
speak to Ian O'Sullivan.

34:50.730 --> 34:55.330
This is O'Sullivan...
