37:23.330 --> 37:26.650
See that? Behind every
great man is his father.

37:41.250 --> 37:44.850
The courier's here.
He's got her. Go find him, Leon!

37:44.930 --> 37:48.610
Mr. O'Sullivan, please...
be calm.

37:48.650 --> 37:51.450
Calm?
Calm, you fucking idiot?

37:51.490 --> 37:53.730
That courier has got videotape of you

37:53.810 --> 37:56.130
chopping off children's hands,
and you want me

37:56.210 --> 37:58.850
- to be fucking calm?!
