37:58.930 --> 38:02.170
Yes, you are part of it!
Don't you remember

38:02.210 --> 38:04.930
where you were before I
dragged you out of the mud?

38:05.010 --> 38:08.810
Yes, I do. And I will
not be going back there.

38:12.050 --> 38:14.890
Get rid of this piece of shit.

38:17.890 --> 38:19.330
Ugh!

38:19.410 --> 38:24.850
Do not do that again, or
