38:26.730 --> 38:29.970
Go on, then.
Go to hell.

38:32.890 --> 38:38.570
- We will see each other again.
- Not if I can help it.

38:40.770 --> 38:41.850
Call the cops. Give
them Leon's description,

38:42.130 --> 38:43.210
tell them where he put Gallagher's body.

38:43.290 --> 38:45.570
I'm going after the goddamn courier!

39:04.930 --> 39:07.050
Can you put this on the big screen?

39:07.130 --> 39:10.970
- I think so.
