42:25.890 --> 42:29.090
<i>Marcus!</i>

42:29.170 --> 42:34.930
Marcus!
It's all lies!

42:38.010 --> 42:41.450
<i>Get out of here! </i>

43:05.370 --> 43:07.490
Hello, transporter.

